release_note: Hi Quiary user : sadly there was a bug in the storage management causing the app to use too much disk space. This has been solved with the newest version. Stay save and healthy Dennis
Hi Quiary user : some typos have been corrected. Stay safe and healthy Dennis

Hi Quiary user : here is a new feature for you. Define two additional daily rating questions. Of course your ratings will also be shown within the chart. I hope you will enjoy this feature as much as I do. Stay safe and healthy Dennis
Hi Quiary user : this update removes all future dates. It especially avoids unnecessary scrolling on iPads at the beginning of a month. Stay safe and healthy Dennis
Hi Quiary user : this update only fixes a bug which shows you the notification screen again and again if you don t activate them. This has been fixed now. Stay safe and healthy Dennis

Hi Quiary user : here is an update for you diary. Now you can choose between 6 main colors and there is an article with 5 tips for writing your diary. I hope you like Quiary even more with this update and I m looking forward to getting your feedback. Stay safe and healthy Dennis

Hi Quiary user : here is an update to view your daily images directly in Quiary. Quiary can show you all pictures of a day saved on your device This also works for the past and dates where you haven t created an entry for You can now swipe through your entries The graph looks much smoother I hope you like Quiary even more with this update and I m looking forward to get your feedback. Stay safe and healthy Dennis

Hi Quiary user : here is an update to better organise and protect your memories with the following new features: Protect your diary with FaceID or TouchID A new lost and found view to find and remember I hope you like Quiary even more with this update and I m looking forward to get your feedback. Stay safe and healthy Dennis
